<section class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-center">
  <div>
    <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-6xl font-black tracking-tight text-zinc-900">
      💎 Mentor the next Rubyist.
      <br>
      <span class="text-rose-600">Or find yours!</span> 🚀
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-6 text-zinc-700 text-xl font-medium">
      <span class="text-red-600 font-bold">Free mentorship</span> connecting early career developers with friendly volunteer mentors from the Ruby community.
      If you're starting out or in your first year of programming, we'll pair you up with an experienced Rubyist who's been where you are! ✨
    </p>
    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
      <%= link_to "🚀 Find a mentor", profiles_path, class: "inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-red-500 to-red-600 px-6 py-3 text-white font-bold text-lg shadow-xl hover:from-red-600 hover:to-red-700 transform hover:scale-105 transition-all ruby-sparkle" %>
      <%= link_to "📝 Request mentorship", new_mentorship_request_path, class: "inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-2xl bg-white px-6 py-3 text-red-700 font-bold text-lg ring-2 ring-red-200 hover:bg-red-50 hover:ring-red-300 transform hover:scale-105 transition-all shadow-lg" %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="relative">
    <div class="absolute -inset-8 -z-10 bg-gradient-to-tr from-red-200 via-red-100 to-red-50 rounded-3xl blur-3xl opacity-60"></div>
    <div class="rounded-3xl border-2 border-zinc-700 bg-zinc-800 p-8 shadow-2xl">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-zinc-700 p-5 border border-zinc-600">
          <p class="text-sm text-rose-400 font-medium">💎 We are nice</p>
          <p class="font-black text-white text-lg">Free mentorship</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-zinc-700 p-5 border border-zinc-600">
          <p class="text-sm text-rose-400 font-medium">🤝 Help wanted</p>
          <p class="font-black text-white text-lg">Anyone can mentor</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-zinc-700 p-5 border border-zinc-600">
          <p class="text-sm text-rose-400 font-medium">🚀 Built with</p>
          <p class="font-black text-white text-lg">Ruby on Rails</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-zinc-700 p-5 border border-zinc-600">
          <p class="text-sm text-rose-400 font-medium">💬 Connect</p>
          <p class="font-black text-white text-lg">Real conversations</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="mt-16 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
  <div class="rounded-3xl border-2 border-zinc-700 bg-zinc-800 p-8 shadow-xl">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-rose-400 mb-4">💎 We are nice</h2>
    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Free mentorship. Always.</h3>
    <p class="text-zinc-300 font-medium leading-relaxed">
      If you're starting out or in your first year of a programming career, we'll pair you up with an existing Rubyist.
      We match you with someone with the experience you're looking for and you can ask whatever you like.
      <span class="text-rose-400 font-bold">No cost, no catch, just community.</span>
    </p>
    <div class="mt-6">
      <%= link_to "🚀 Find your mentor", profiles_path, class: "inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl bg-rose-600 px-4 py-2 text-white font-bold hover:bg-rose-700 transition-colors shadow-lg" %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="rounded-3xl border-2 border-zinc-700 bg-zinc-800 p-8 shadow-xl">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-rose-400 mb-4">🤝 Help wanted</h2>
    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Anyone can be a mentor.</h3>
    <p class="text-zinc-300 font-medium leading-relaxed">
      Every working Ruby developer has experiences to offer to those following us into our community.
      You only need a year of programming before you can give back.
      <span class="text-rose-400 font-bold">Share your journey, help someone else's.</span>
    </p>
    <div class="mt-6">
      <%= link_to "✨ Become a mentor", new_profile_path, class: "inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl bg-zinc-700 px-4 py-2 text-white font-bold border border-zinc-600 hover:bg-zinc-600 transition-colors shadow-lg" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
